text: Joseph E. Tata (September 13, 1936 â€“ August 24, 2022) was an American actor. He was known for his role as Nat Bussichio in the television series Beverly Hills, 90210. He died on August 24, 2022 from the disease, three weeks before his 86th birthday in Los Angeles, California. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Deaths from Alzheimer's disease Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Los Angeles Category:American stage actors
